<exercise id="fs-idm241623104">
<problem id="fs-idm238318656">
<para id="fs-idm230002752"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68083"/>Remarkable Enterprises requires four units of part A for every unit of A1 that it produces. Currently, part A is made by Remarkable, with these per-unit costs in a month when 4,000 units were produced:</para>
